# Visualization Spec — {{PROCESS_NAME}}

> **L5 — Process Visualization**: Diagram conventions for this process.
> Must reference L1.4 (step sequence) and L1.7 (RACIO matrix) for auto-rendering.

---

## Diagram Type

- **Primary Type**: {{PRIMARY_DIAGRAM_TYPE}} (swimlane / flowchart / value_stream_map)
- **Vibe Keywords**: {{VIBE_KEYWORDS}} (e.g., "operator-first", "compliance-emphasis")

---

## Color Semantics

| Element | Color | Hex | Applies To |
|---|---|---|---|
| Manual Step | {{COLOR_MANUAL}} | {{HEX_MANUAL}} | Steps executed by human operator |
| Automated Step | {{COLOR_AUTO}} | {{HEX_AUTO}} | Steps executed by system/API |
| Decision Point | {{COLOR_DECISION}} | {{HEX_DECISION}} | Diamond/gateway nodes |
| Exception Path | {{COLOR_EXCEPTION}} | {{HEX_EXCEPTION}} | .E steps, error flows |
| Handoff | {{COLOR_HANDOFF}} | {{HEX_HANDOFF}} | Cross-role or cross-process transitions |
| Success Terminal | {{COLOR_SUCCESS}} | {{HEX_SUCCESS}} | Happy-path end states |

---

## Naming Convention

- **Step Label Format**: `<b>{{STEP_ID}}</b><br/>{{STEP_NAME}}`
- **Max Characters per Node**: {{MAX_CHARS}} (recommended: 30-40)
- **Step Prefix**: {{STEP_NAME_PREFIX}} (verb / noun / id)

